rows.label: bf11380100_0010
rows.name: Ahoy! Miss me?

rows.label: bf11380100_0020
rows.name: Adel-sama?

rows.label: bf11380100_0030
rows.name: Adel-sama's finally come back!

rows.label: bf11380100_0040
rows.name: Welcome back, Adel-sama!

rows.label: bf11380100_0050
rows.name:
Wow...
Someone's got himself a bit of a fan club.

rows.label: bf11380100_0060
rows.name:
Maybe that's why he decided to take
action, to wield that love for good.

rows.label: bf11380100_0070
rows.name:
By the way... Adel gave the order to
meet in this place specifically, right?

rows.label: bf11380100_0080
rows.name: What's so special about it?

rows.label: bf11380100_0090
rows.name: This land is Adel's domain.

rows.label: bf11380100_0100
rows.name: Look, that over there is his manor.

rows.label: bf11380100_0110
rows.name: Hahh... Certainly fit for a prince.

rows.label: bf11380100_0120
rows.name: Eh, it could stand to be bigger.

rows.label: bf11380100_0125
rows.name: And, you know, not in the middle of nowhere...

rows.label: bf11380100_0130
rows.name:
Are you completely incapable of
saying something without sarcasm?

rows.label: bf11380100_0140
rows.name:
Sorry, it's just how I am.
I don't really think I can help it.

rows.label: bf11380100_0150
rows.name:
She's right, though. It is quite a
way from the capital.

rows.label: bf11380100_0160
rows.name: He is far too esteemed for his own good.

rows.label: bf11380100_0170
rows.name:
Fourth in line to the throne,
but loved by soldiers and citizens...

rows.label: bf11380100_0180
rows.name:
His relations with High Prince Zettar
are quite strained as a result, I hear.

rows.label: bf11380100_0190
rows.name:
Really?
I suppose even princes have problems.
